                        Example: "Iâ€™m Betty Phipps, a second-year Computer Science major at Florida State University, with a deep passion for leveraging technology to solve real-world problems. I have a keen interest in data science, investment banking, and technical consulting, as well as a drive to contribute to sustainability efforts through innovative tech solutions."
        - **Career Goals:** Discuss where you want your career to go, mentioning your goal to work for Royal Caribbean and your interest in sustainability, technology, and business.
            - Example: "My career goals include applying my technical expertise to support sustainable initiatives, such as Royal Caribbean's 'Sustaining Our Planet' initiative, while building a strong foundation in investment banking and data science."
        - **Personal Brand:** Emphasize your qualities, such as your passion for growth, adaptability, collaboration, and continuous learning.
                        </p>
                        </article>
                    </Col>
                </row>
            </container>
        </section>
 )
}
